     "Computing one cofactor, e.g. $C_{11}=\\det\\begin{pmatrix}2&1\\\\0&2\\end{pmatrix}=4$, fixes $(A^{-1})_{11}=4/9$, matching the polynomial result; computing the full adjugate gives $\\operatorname{adj}A=\\begin{pmatrix}4&-2&1\\\\1&4&-2\\\\-2&1&4\\end{pmatrix}$.",
