     "**Case $a\\notin\\{1,-2\\}$:** $\\operatorname{rank} M=3$, so a unique solution exists. By symmetry $x=y=z=s$; any equation gives $(a+2)s=1$, hence $x=y=z=\\frac{1}{a+2}.$",
