  "answer": "\\operatorname{rank} B_n = \\begin{cases} n-1, & n\\equiv 2 \\pmod 3,\\\\[2pt] n, & n\\not\\equiv 2 \\pmod 3.\\end{cases}\\qquad\\bigl(\\det B_n=1,0,-1,-1,0,1\\text{ for }n=1,2,3,4,5,6,\\text{ then period }6\\bigr)",
