     "$\\operatorname{rank} B_n=n-\\#\\{k:\\,1+2\\cos\\frac{k\\pi}{n+1}=0\\}.$ The condition $\\cos\\frac{k\\pi}{n+1}=-\\tfrac12$ means $\\frac{k\\pi}{n+1}=\\frac{2\\pi}{3}$, i.e. $3k=2(n+1).$",
