  "statement": "Consider the $4\\times 4$ block matrix with $2\\times 2$ blocks\n$$M=\\begin{pmatrix} A & B \\\\ C & D \\end{pmatrix},\\quad A=\\begin{pmatrix}2&1\\\\0&2\\end{pmatrix},\\ B=\\begin{pmatrix}1&0\\\\1&1\\end{pmatrix},\\ C=\\begin{pmatrix}0&1\\\\2&0\\end{pmatrix},\\ D=\\begin{pmatrix}3&1\\\\0&3\\end{pmatrix}.$$\nCompute $\\det M$, and compare with the (incorrect) value $\\det(AD-BC)$.",
