     "This realizes the identity as a commutator precisely because $\\operatorname{tr}(I_2)=2=0$ in $\\mathbb{F}_2$ — and the single 'defective' entry $-1$ becomes $+1$ exactly because $\\operatorname{char}=2$.",
     "In characteristic $0$ the same trace count gives $\\operatorname{tr}(I_2)=2\\neq 0$, blocking any solution; and the entry $-1$ would not equal $+1$, so even the construction collapses. $\\blacksquare$"
