  "statement": "Let $A=uv^{\\top}$ be a nonzero rank-one matrix in $M_n(\\mathbb{C})$ with $u,v\\in\\mathbb{C}^n$ column vectors, and set $t=\\operatorname{tr}(A)=v^{\\top}u$. Prove that $\\operatorname{tr}(A^k)=t^k$ for all $k\\ge1$, and that $\\det(I_n+A)=1+t$. Determine all such $A$ for which $A$ is idempotent.",
