     "Thus the eigenvalue multiset is $\\{t,0,\\dots,0\\}$ (if $t=0$ these merge into an all-zero, nilpotent spectrum). Since each $\\operatorname{tr}(A^k)=\\sum\\lambda_i^{\\,k}$, we get $\\operatorname{tr}(A^k)=t^k+0=t^k$.",
