     "Subtracting the two relations gives $AB-BA=0$, i.e. $AB=BA$. Combined with $AB+BA=0$ this forces $2AB=0$, so $AB=BA=0$. Conversely, if $AB=BA=0$ then $AB+BA=0$ and $A+B$ is idempotent. This proves the equivalence.",
