  "statement": "Let $P,Q \\in M_n(\\mathbb{R})$ be orthogonal projections ($P=P^{\\top}=P^2,\\ Q=Q^{\\top}=Q^2$). Prove the chain $$0 \\le \\operatorname{tr}(PQ) \\le \\min\\{\\operatorname{tr}(P),\\operatorname{tr}(Q)\\},$$ and determine the equality cases at both ends.",
