     "There are at most $m=\\min\\{\\operatorname{rank}P,\\operatorname{rank}Q\\}$ terms, each $\\le1$, so $\\operatorname{tr}(PQ)\\le\\min\\{\\operatorname{rank}P,\\operatorname{rank}Q\\}$.",
