  "statement": "Let $A=\\begin{pmatrix} p & q \\\\ r & s \\end{pmatrix}$ be a real $2\\times 2$ matrix whose two **columns** $c_1=\\binom{p}{r}$ and $c_2=\\binom{q}{s}$ are arbitrary nonzero vectors. Prove that\n$$\\bigl|\\det A\\bigr|\\;\\le\\;\\|c_1\\|\\,\\|c_2\\|,$$\nand determine exactly when equality holds.",
