     "Since $F_{n+1}\\ge 2$ for $n\\ge 2$ while $\\det(B_n)\\in\\{-1,0,1\\}$, the two quantities never coincide for $n\\ge 2$. $\\boxed{\\operatorname{per}(B_n)=F_{n+1},\\quad \\det(B_n)\\ \\text{period-}6,\\ \\text{never equal for }n\\ge 2}$"
