     "$A\\chi_S=(d-2|S|)\\chi_S$, so the eigenvalue is $d-2|S|$ and there are $\\binom{d}{|S|}$ sets of each size, recovering the spectrum $\\{d-2j\\}$ with multiplicity $\\binom dj$.",
     "Thus $\\operatorname{tr}(A^k)=\\sum_S (d-2|S|)^k=\\sum_{j=0}^d\\binom dj(d-2j)^k$ and per-vertex it is $1/2^d$ of this. $\\boxed{\\operatorname{tr}(A^k)=\\sum_j\\binom dj(d-2j)^k}$"
