  "statement": "Let $p$ be a prime. Find the number of idempotent matrices $A\\in M_2(\\mathbb{F}_p)$, i.e. those satisfying $$A^2 = A,$$ as a closed-form polynomial in $p$.",
  "answer": "$$\\boxed{\\,p^2 + p + 2\\,}$$ idempotent matrices: the two scalars $0$ and $I$, plus $p(p+1)$ matrices of rank $1$.",
