     "Then $\\prod_{k=0}^{n-1}(3-2\\cos\\theta_k)=\\alpha^{-n}\\prod_{k}(\\alpha-\\omega^k)\\prod_k(\\alpha-\\bar\\omega^k)$. Since $\\prod_k(\\alpha-\\omega^k)=\\alpha^n-1$ and $\\prod_k(\\alpha-\\omega^{-k})=\\alpha^n-1$ (the conjugate roots are the same set), the product is $\\alpha^{-n}(\\alpha^n-1)^2$.",
